overrideValues.value: Theme Editor scales typefaces to Material typescale specifications based on x-height. Type symbols are used in components.
Theme Editor generates a 50-900 Tonal Palette for your Primary and Secondary colors. Override the color used in any Component Symbol for the ones you see in your Tonal Palette using Sketch Overrides.

Download each System Icon set in the Theme Editor Icon tab. After you download a Preset System Icon file, select "File" > "Save as Library" in the Sketch Toolbar to use the full set of icons with this file.
Shadows are saved as Symbols in this file and as Shared Styles. Use these shadows as a reference for custom symbols you create.
To view all themed components go to the "Material Components" Page of this file. Not all components are affected by your theme inputs.
